    "description_long": "This is a stylized human figure dressed as a construction worker, featuring a blue wide-brimmed hat, a yellow short-sleeve shirt, and blue checkered shorts. The figure carries a large orange backpack with a rolled mat on top and a visible NASA logo on the back. Accessories include a green pouch on the left hip and a brown belt with a pouch on the right. The figure wears yellow and blue work boots and has a harness or strap system across the chest and shoulders. The overall appearance is cartoonish and low-poly, with exaggerated proportions and simplified facial features.",
